{"name":"Mathlib.Tactic.ToAdditive","instances":[{"typeNames":["ToAdditive.ValueType"],"name":"ToAdditive.instReprValueType","className":"Repr"}],"imports":["Init","Mathlib.Data.String.Defs","Mathlib.Lean.Expr.Basic","Mathlib.Lean.Expr.ReplaceRec","Mathlib.Lean.Expr","Mathlib.Lean.NameMapAttribute","Lean","Lean.Data"],"declarations":[{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/ToAdditive.lean#L439-L445","name":"ToAdditive.proceedFields","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/ToAdditive.html#ToAdditive.proceedFields","doc":"Add the structure fields of `src` to the translations dictionary\nso that future uses of `to_additive` will map them to the corresponding `tgt` fields. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/ToAdditive.lean#L411-L426","name":"ToAdditive.targetName","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/ToAdditive.html#ToAdditive.targetName","doc":"Return the provided target name or autogenerate one if one was not provided. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/ToAdditive.lean#L404-L408","name":"ToAdditive.guessName","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/ToAdditive.html#ToAdditive.guessName","doc":"Autogenerate target name for `to_additive`. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/ToAdditive.lean#L364-L366","name":"ToAdditive.addCommPrefix","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/ToAdditive.html#ToAdditive.addCommPrefix","doc":"`add_comm_prefix x s` returns `\"comm_\" ++ s` if `x = tt` and `s` otherwise. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/ToAdditive.lean#L361-L361","name":"ToAdditive.instReprValueType","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/ToAdditive.html#ToAdditive.instReprValueType","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/ToAdditive.lean#L348-L361","name":"ToAdditive.ValueType","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/ToAdditive.html#ToAdditive.ValueType","doc":"`ValueType` is the type of the arguments that can be provided to `to_additive`. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/ToAdditive.lean#L327-L344","name":"ToAdditive.firstMultiplicativeArg","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/ToAdditive.html#ToAdditive.firstMultiplicativeArg","doc":"Find the first argument of `nm` that has a multiplicative type-class on it.\nReturns 1 if there are no types with a multiplicative class as arguments.\nE.g. `prod.group` returns 1, and `pi.has_one` returns 2.\n"},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/ToAdditive.lean#L311-L321","name":"ToAdditive.transformDecl","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/ToAdditive.html#ToAdditive.transformDecl","doc":"Make a new copy of a declaration, replacing fragments of the names of identifiers in the type and\nthe body using the `translations` dictionary.\nThis is used to implement `@[to_additive]`.\n"},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/ToAdditive.lean#L292-L304","name":"ToAdditive.copyAttributes","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/ToAdditive.html#ToAdditive.copyAttributes","doc":"This should copy all of the attributes on src to tgt.\nAt the moment it only copies `simp` attributes because attributes\nare not stored by the environment.\n\n[todo] add more attributes. A change is coming to core that should\nallow us to iterate the attributes applied to a given decalaration.\n"},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/ToAdditive.lean#L245-L283","name":"ToAdditive.transformDeclAux","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/ToAdditive.html#ToAdditive.transformDeclAux","doc":"transform the declaration `src` and all declarations `pre._proof_i` occurring in `src`\nusing the transforms dictionary.\n`replace_all`, `trace`, `ignore` and `reorder` are configuration options.\n`pre` is the declaration that got the `@[to_additive]` attribute and `tgt_pre` is the target of this\ndeclaration. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/ToAdditive.lean#L236-L238","name":"ToAdditive.isInternal'","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/ToAdditive.html#ToAdditive.isInternal'","doc":"Lean 4 makes declarations which are not internal\n(that is, head string starts with `_`) but which should be transformed.\neg `proof_1` in `Lean.Meta.mkAuxDefinitionFor` this might be better fixed in core.\nThis method is polyfill for that. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/ToAdditive.lean#L223-L230","name":"ToAdditive.updateDecl","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/ToAdditive.html#ToAdditive.updateDecl","doc":"Run applyReplacementFun on the given `srcDecl` to make a new declaration with name `tgt` "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/ToAdditive.lean#L201-L220","name":"ToAdditive.expand","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/ToAdditive.html#ToAdditive.expand","doc":"`e.expand` eta-expands all expressions that have as head a constant `n` in\n`reorder`. They are expanded until they are applied to one more argument than the maximum in\n`reorder.find n`. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/ToAdditive.lean#L195-L196","name":"ToAdditive.etaExpandN","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/ToAdditive.html#ToAdditive.etaExpandN","doc":"Eta expands `e` at most `n` times."},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/ToAdditive.lean#L152-L192","name":"ToAdditive.applyReplacementFun","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/ToAdditive.html#ToAdditive.applyReplacementFun","doc":"`e.applyReplacementFun f test` applies `f` to each identifier\n(inductive type, defined function etc) in an expression, unless\n* The identifier occurs in an application with first argument `arg`; and\n* `test arg` is false.\nHowever, if `f` is in the dictionary `relevant`, then the argument `relevant.find f`\nis tested, instead of the first argument.\n\nReorder contains the information about what arguments to reorder:\ne.g. `g x₁ x₂ x₃ ... xₙ` becomes `g x₂ x₁ x₃ ... xₙ` if `reorder.find g = some [1]`.\nWe assume that all functions where we want to reorder arguments are fully applied.\nThis can be done by applying `etaExpand` first.\n"},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/ToAdditive.lean#L133-L137","name":"ToAdditive.additiveTest","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/ToAdditive.html#ToAdditive.additiveTest","doc":"`additiveTest e` tests whether the expression `e` contains no constant\n`nm` that is not applied to any arguments, and such that `translations.find?[nm] = none`.\nThis is used in `@[to_additive]` for deciding which subexpressions to transform: we only transform\nconstants if `additiveTest` applied to their first argument returns `true`.\nThis means we will replace expression applied to e.g. `α` or `α × β`, but not when applied to\ne.g. `Nat` or `ℝ × α`.\nWe ignore all arguments specified by the `ignore` `NameMap`.\nIf `replaceAll` is `true` the test always returns `true`.\n"},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/ToAdditive.lean#L100-L101","name":"ToAdditive.replaceAll","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/ToAdditive.html#ToAdditive.replaceAll","doc":"Get whether or not the replace-all flag is set. If this is true, then the\nadditiveTest heuristic is not used and all instances of multiplication are replaced.\nYou can enable this with `@[to_additive!]`"},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/ToAdditive.lean#L91-L95","name":"ToAdditive.insertTranslation","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/ToAdditive.html#ToAdditive.insertTranslation","doc":"Add a (multiplicative → additive) name translation to the translations map. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/ToAdditive.lean#L87-L88","name":"ToAdditive.findTranslation?","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/ToAdditive.html#ToAdditive.findTranslation?","doc":"Get the multiplicative → additive translation for the given name. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/ToAdditive.lean#L83-L83","name":"ToAdditive.translations","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/ToAdditive.html#ToAdditive.translations","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/ToAdditive.lean#L77-L80","name":"ToAdditive.isRelevant","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/ToAdditive.html#ToAdditive.isRelevant","doc":"Given a declaration name and an argument index, determines whether it\nis relevant. This is used in `applyReplacementFun` where more detail on what it\ndoes can be found. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/ToAdditive.lean#L65-L65","name":"ToAdditive.relevantArgAttr","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/ToAdditive.html#ToAdditive.relevantArgAttr","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/ToAdditive.lean#L62-L63","name":"ToAdditive.shouldReorder","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/ToAdditive.html#ToAdditive.shouldReorder","doc":"Given a declaration name and an argument index, determines whether this index\nshould be swapped with the next one. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/ToAdditive.lean#L57-L58","name":"ToAdditive.getReorder","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/ToAdditive.html#ToAdditive.getReorder","doc":"Get the reorder list (defined using `@[to_additive_reorder ...]`) for the given declaration. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/ToAdditive.lean#L47-L47","name":"ToAdditive.reorderAttr","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/ToAdditive.html#ToAdditive.reorderAttr","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/ToAdditive.lean#L44-L45","name":"ToAdditive.ignore","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/ToAdditive.html#ToAdditive.ignore","doc":"Gets the set of arguments that should be ignored for the given name\n(according to `@[to_additive_ignore_args ...]`).\nThis value is used in `additiveTestAux`. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/ToAdditive.lean#L30-L30","name":"ToAdditive.ignoreArgsAttr","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/ToAdditive.html#ToAdditive.ignoreArgsAttr","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/ToAdditive.lean#L23-L23","name":"to_additive","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/ToAdditive.html#to_additive","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/ToAdditive.lean#L22-L22","name":"to_additive_reorder","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/ToAdditive.html#to_additive_reorder","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/ToAdditive.lean#L21-L21","name":"to_additive_relevant_arg","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/ToAdditive.html#to_additive_relevant_arg","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/ToAdditive.lean#L20-L20","name":"to_additive_ignore_args","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/ToAdditive.html#to_additive_ignore_args","doc":""}]}